        target="Google account">here</a>.
      </section>
      
      <!-- Browser Support
      ================================================== -->
      <section id="browser-support">
        <div class="page-header">
          <h1>Browser Support</h1>
        </div>
        
        NetLAB works best on modern browsers and some features only
        work on the most recent versions of some of these browsers.
        
        <h3>Supported Browsers</h3>
        We recommend the most recent release of <a href="https://www.google.com/intl/en/chrome/browser/">Chrome</a>.
        <br>If you want to
        use <a href="http://www.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/new/">Firefox</a>
        it is possible that some characters like "-", "_" don't work
        on consoles of virtual machines.
        <br>It is possible to support Internet Explorer. However we do not test at all regularly on Internet Explorer.
      </section>
    
